intervals <- findInterval(getValues(ras_res), quantiles)

pa_ecoregions %>% 
  group_by(US_L3CODE) %>%

      st_sf() %>%
      return()
  })) ->
  pa_ecoregions_nested

  unnest(cols = c(data)) %>%
  st_sf() %>%
  st_transform(4326) ->
